<div class="banner group"><img class="align-left" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/students-on-steps.jpg" />
<div class="banner-content">
<h2>Congratulations!</h2>
<p>Now that you have been admitted, you can start your preparations to attend BYU-Idaho. Use this guide to access helpful resources and links, including:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="x30305.xml">Your Student Ambassador</a></li>
<li><a href="x50436.xml">New Student Checklist</a></li>
<li><a href="x30290.xml">Parent Information</a></li>
<li><a href="x18876.xml">Deferral Information</a></li>
<li><a href="x43245.xml">Get Connected (New Student Orientation)</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="top group">
<h3>Your Student Ambassador is Here to Help You!</h3>
<div class="arrow down-arrow"></div>
</div>
<div class="content group"><img class="align-right" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/student-ambassador.jpg" />
<p>A <a href="x30305.xml">Student Ambassador</a> will be assigned to you upon accepting your offer. They will:</p>
<ul>
<li>Be your first point of contact with BYU-Idaho</li>
<li>Guide you through the <a href="x50436.xml">New Student Checklist</a></li>
<li>Help answer your questions and direct you to campus services and resources</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="top group">
<h3>New Student Checklist</h3>
<div class="arrow down-arrow"></div>
</div>
<div class="content group"><img class="align-right" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/student-checklist.jpg" />
<p>The <a href="x50436.xml">New Student Checklist</a> outlines key steps you need to complete prior to starting classes. Links, videos and detailed information in the checklist will help you with these steps. Items include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Scholarships</li>
<li>Housing</li>
<li>Registration dates and Information</li>
<li>Move-in Day / Get Connected dates</li>
<li>Academic Advising</li>
<li><a href="x50436.xml">And More!</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="top group">
<h3>Get Connected</h3>
<div class="arrow down-arrow"></div>
</div>
<div class="content group"><img class="align-left" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/get-connected_06.jpg" />
<div class="get-connected-content">
<p><a href="x43245.xml">Get Connected</a> (New Student Orientation) serves as the official start to your BYU-Idaho experience.</p>
<p>Events include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Move-in day (<a href="x43483.xml">See Schedule</a>)</li>
<li>Housing</li>
<li>Registration dates and Information</li>
<li>Move-in Day / Get Connected dates</li>
<li>Academic Advising</li>
<li><a href="x43483.xml">And More!</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="top group">
<h3>Visit Days</h3>
<div class="arrow down-arrow"></div>
</div>
<div class="content group"><img class="align-right" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/visit-days.jpg" />
<p>Want to visit campus and get a better feel for the University? <a href="https://creator.zoho.com/ambassadors/sign-up-form/form-perma/Sign_up_form/">Sign up</a> for a customized visit day, options include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Attend a class</li>
<li>Explore housing options</li>
<li>Meet with an Academic Advisor</li>
<li>Move-in Day / Get Connected dates</li>
<li><a href="x37137.xml">And More!</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="top group">
<h3>Parents</h3>
<div class="arrow down-arrow"></div>
</div>
<div class="content group"><img class="align-right" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/parents.jpg" />
<p>Parents of new students can stay connected to BYU-Idaho, access parent resources and get important information by visiting the <a href="x30290.xml">parents' portal</a>.</p>
<div class="defer-cta"><img src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/student-support/get-prepared/defer.png" />
<p>Leaving on a Mission? Be sure to <a href="x18876.xml">defer your offer</a> so you don't lose your spot.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="page-footer">
<div class="student-support-office group">
<h2>Student Support Office</h2>
<ul class="contact-links">
<li><a href="mailto:studentambassadors@byui.edu">studentambassadors@byui.edu</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.byui.edu/student-support/student-ambassadors">Student Ambassadors</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/BYUIstudentambassadors">Facebook Page</a></li>
</ul>
<ul class="contact-location">
<li>Rigby Hall 272</li>
<li><a href="tel:2084961420">(208) 496-1420</a></li>
</ul>
